differences.actualValue: <speak>I'm sorry to hear that you're having trouble reaching the customer. Since you are already at the drop off location, you can start the timer by calling, or texting the customer. When the timer expires, you'll be paid for the delivery. You'll also need to return to the store to return the alcohol. Do not leave the alcohol at the door. Don't worry -- you'll be paid for the return trip as well.<break time="750ms"/></speak><speak>To listen to this message again, just say, repeat it. <break time="700ms"/> Is there anything else I can help you with today?</speak>

When the timer expires, you'll be paid for the delivery. You'll also need to return to the store to return the alcohol. Do not leave the alcohol at the door. Don't worry -- you'll be paid for the return trip as well.<break time="750ms"/></speak>
